    - target: {fileID: 5420115657269891386, guid: 5ddd7e9d3f12a9a439a2e2c43e7cb1ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Earth is special because it is one of the rare planets which has practiced
        the art of archery in their past. Many planets need to contend with their
        biology or construct special gravity fields which increase/decrease their
        gravity so they can practice this art. With earth, the previous existence
        of archery means that Earth has the perfect conditions as well as the perfect
        biology to play this sport.
